                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-145-victim792 t18260112-145-viclabel822"></join>; the prisoner lived with us three weeks, as <rs id="t18260112-145-deflabel823" type="occupation">errand-boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-145-defend790 t18260112-145-deflabel823"></join> - it was his duty to receive money for us. - Sarah Ann Bull owed me 15s. 6d; I sent him for it nearly two months ago; I asked if he had received it - he said he had not, but the lady would call and pay me; he left a fortnight afterwards. I thought it was not all right, and went myself, and saw his receipt to the bill.</p>
