                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner on the 20th of December - he said he had taken the money, and lost it - he was a neighbour, and bore a good character. I believe he got playing with some boys, and lost the money.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I lost the money, and did not tell my mistress - I thought my father could make it up.</p>
